{"tid":700309,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"挪威人口智商自 1970 年有下跌跡象","createTime":"2018-06-13T08:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T09:44:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3a8524151c16e80d335c82fe4a2bfc6f45d669","tid":700309,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"挪威研究🇨🇳人員🇨🇳發現當地智商水平在過去 10 年有下跌趨勢。研究已刊於《美國國家科學院期刊 (PNAS) 》。<br />\n<br />\n過往研究曾發現人類智商在過去逐年提升，並稱此現象為費林效應 (Flynn Effect) 。以往科學家認為，智商上升可能跟營養吸收有改善、教育水平上升及醫療制度更完善等因素引起。然而，部份已發展國家的智商水平在近年開始有下跌趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n最新一項研究分析了挪威收集的 730,000 個、共三代人的智商數據，他們發現當地年輕人的智商水平在 1970-2009 年期間，出現下跌跡象&mdash;&mdash;平均每代人下跌約 7 分，回到 70 年前的水平。今次數據也與 2016 年綜述多個已發展國家智商數據研究發現的智商下跌趨勢相近。<br />\n<br />\n今次研究🇨🇳人員🇨🇳分析數據後認為，下跌趨勢可能主要與環境因素相關，而非基因或移民等因素。不過，現時研究🇨🇳人員🇨🇳尚未能確認當地年輕人智商水平下跌確切成因，但初步估計跟教育制度改變、閱讀量減少等因素相關。<br />\n<br />\n《衛報》曾訪問發現全球智商在 20 世紀有所上升的 James Flynn，他曾指出智商水平與環境因素有相當大的關係。以多明尼加為例，當地基建每 10 年就遭天災破壞，均會令當地人的智商水平難以追得上其他已發展國家。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n智商是預測日後成功機會的重要指標之一，因此今次研究不得不令科學家更進一步了解，為甚麼近年已發展國家年輕人的智商，有開始下降的趨勢。 <br />\n<br />\n來源：<br />\n<a href=\"http://Phys.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPhys.org&d=FV2XEAZaZhoVNZDUrCLvDaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=98578761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Phys.org</a>, Researchers find IQ scores dropping since the 1970s, 12 June 2018<br />\n<br />\n報告：<br />\nBratsberg, B. &amp; Rogeberg, O. (2018). Flynn effect and its reversal are both environmentally caused. PNAS, published ahead of print June 11, 2018. DOI: 10.1073/pnas.1718793115<br />\n<br />\n文／Edward Ho、審核／Alan Chiu<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/cosmos/%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%99%BA%E5%95%86%E8%87%AA-1970%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C%E8%B7%A1%E8%B1%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fcosmos%2F%25E6%258C%25AA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%25A3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%2587%25AA-1970%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25B7%258C%25E8%25B7%25A1%25E8%25B1%25A1%2F&d=FV2XEAZaZhoVNZDUrCLvDaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=39f0f4c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fcosmos%2F%25E6%258C%25AA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%25A3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%2587%25AA-1970%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25B7%258C%25E8%25B7%25A1%25E8%25B1%25A1%2F&h=e7c143db\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/cosmos/%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%99%BA%E5%95%86%E8%87%AA-1970%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C%E8%B7%A1%E8%B1%A1/</a>"},{"pid":"47fb182a57e21dda4a678ce8f155c78a8474da92","tid":700309,"uid":186268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:06:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e244321f55b14cf4c42adfbcf2bc4f7406be06e8","tid":700309,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"研究人員都當蝗語？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a046c17c3d3fdae068b9433d6bde4ba6e4c5a3a0","tid":700309,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e244321f55b14cf4c42adfbcf2bc4f7406be06e8","tid":700309,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"研究人員都當蝗語？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec78150f844cad59c165c71ae200f948690d290a","tid":700309,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"引入多D香港人囉"},{"pid":"8485964d2aba509b7a1e8e69bf31a5712ee0d064","tid":700309,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:35:17.000Z","msg":"唔差在研究下德國啦<br />\n啲人咁鍾意welcome rapefugees<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif